title: Working to Advance the Equality of Women in Business
itunes:title: Working to Advance the Equality of Women in Business
description:
Liz Elting, CEO and Founder of the Elizabeth Elting Foundation, discusses funding for women-centric businesses through the Endless Frontier Labs program.
Hosts: Paul Sweeney and Kriti Gupta. Producer: Paul Brennan.
